  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "2. In a small bowl, mix together chopped chive, smoked paprika, and salt.",
    "3. In a pan over medium heat, heat olive oil and sauté minced garlic until fragrant.",
    "4. Add the chive mixture to the pan and cook for 1-2 minutes.",
    "5. Remove from heat and stir in lemon juice and mayonnaise.",
    "6. Season with black pepper to taste.",
    "7. Serve warm or at room temperature.",
    "8. Enjoy!"
  ],
